Wikimedia Bangladesh Foundation (aka Wikimedia Bangladesh or WikimediaBD) is a registered charity established to support volunteers in Bangladesh who work on Wikimedia projects such as Wikipedia. It is a Wikimedia chapter approved by the Wikimedia Foundation which owns and hosts those projects.
The chapter has several collaborations with educational and other institutions and has organized events for the volunteers aimed at adding content to Foundation projects.
It has a temporary office in Dhaka, Bangladesh.
